ERROR:FUNCTION_WITHOUT_ARGS: Bad function definition - void barrier() should probably be void barrier(void)
#67: FILE: kernel/hd.c:324:
+void barrier();

Function declarations without arguments like::

  int foo()

should be::

  int foo(void)

